  "texts": [
    "If p(j 1 |x) < p(j 2 |x), j 1 ̸ = j 2 ̸ = y, then ∂L NNCE ∂p(j 1 |x) > ∂L NNCE ∂p(j 2 |x).Proof.",
    "As per the assumption that p(j 1 |x) < p(j 2 |x), we have:1 p(j 1 |x) > 1 p(j 2 |x).",
